In the Matter of CHEZ MARIANNE, Inc., Debtor, John W. REMER, as Trustee, etc., Appellant. No. 222. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. Nov. 22, 1935. Abraham L. Freeman, of New York City’ for appellant. Samuel C. Duberstein, of Brooklyn, N. Y., for appellee.

Before MANTON, L. HAND, and SWAN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed in open court
